## EnchantPlus Plugin Information
- **Version**: 2.0.0
- **Release**: Level System + Critical Bug Fixes
- **Total Enchantments**: 22 (All with Level I-III variants)
- **Status**: Production Ready
- **Features**: Complete Level System, Performance Optimizations, Bug Fixes
- **Compatibility**: PaperMC 1.20.x+
- **Java Version**: 17+

This plugin includes a comprehensive enchantment system with:
- 22 unique enchantments across 5 rarity tiers
- Level I-III progression system for all enchantments
- Performance-optimized async operations
- Thread-safe data structures
- Memory leak prevention
- Comprehensive bug fixes
- Production-ready stability

For detailed documentation, see EnchantPlus-Guide.md
